text: Groslée is a former commune in the Ain department in eastern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune Groslée-Saint-Benoît.Arrêté préfectoral 30 December 2015 ==Population== ==See also== *Communes of the Ain department *Lac de Crotel ==References== Category:Former communes of Ain Category:Ain communes articles needing translation from French Wikipedia Category:Populated places disestablished in 2016
